track.name: Drift
comments: I am a guy. I like this track.

i am woman, living in a very old city full of decaying beauty. living in this city is intense because we expect it will all be gone sometime in the near future. once it's gone, all that will remain are the spirits. no sounds, no smells, nobody. this too is my soundtrack.

i am an young, young man living in a vibrant and invigorating city. i do not know if those who populate the streets are man or machines, but i can see they look like me, they look lost and always to busy. But i awake and see a door and an empty room. This is my soundtrack, indeed.

I am an old, old man living in a yurt in a dark and unrelenting forest. i am sure that all around me are deer but i never see them, all i see is images of my past lives and loves. i dream of impulses and tics. This is my soundtrack.
